extendedInfo.description: Log each time your baby has a feeding. Log each wet/bowl event and track which breast was used.  Keep up to date with your log so you know exactly if your baby is producing the correct amount of events.View feeding/wet/bowel history by day

reviews.title: Love it
reviews.comment: Keeps me organized and very simple to use ! Quick and easy perfect for this new mom.
reviews.author: A Google User

reviews.comment: Good app, but it doesn\'t allow you to edit info you\'ve entered or enter info for past days. Needs a note section for expressed milk.
